### These functions are regularly maintained by the author (Lizzy Steell). There are additional functions here that
### are not included in the R code supporting the article 'Revealing patterns of homoplasy in discrete phylogenetic
### datasets with a cross-comparable index'. 

### If you have issues, please email lizzysteell@gmail.com explaining the problem.

### As of 21-Oct-2025, these functions have been migrated to the phylodisc project (https://github.com/LizzySteell/phylodisc/new/main/functions)
### This project will be developed into the phylodisc R package and the code will be developed in that repository
